<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Gold_Certificates_and_Silver_Notes"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Gold Certificates and Silver Notes</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="#The_problem_with_Gold"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">The problem with Gold</span></a></li>
